                                                                <div data-widget-id="wid__image__5b1671430d9ff" class="moto-widget moto-widget-image moto-preset-default moto-align-center moto-spacing-top-auto moto-spacing-right-auto moto-spacing-bottom-small moto-spacing-left-auto  " data-widget="image">
                                                                    <span class="moto-widget-image-link">
